{"tid":332141,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完英超四角賽真係好唏噓","createTime":"2017-07-22T18:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T04:11:41.000Z","uid":123320,"like":113,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30ef01993d1cd66962698c7cefcb03cd6098bd71","tid":332141,"uid":123320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"如果今日到場嘅利迷可以用今日嘅投入同熱情支持港隊就好喇<br />\n睇英超同睇本地波冇抵觸，我唔知道利物浦曼聯代表到你地。 但我淨係知道港隊真係完全代表到我 我想同港隊經歷每一場贏同輸  港隊提醒返我 我係香港人 儘管呢個地方有好多不是 但我都好愛呢個地方<br />\n如果你地都愛呢個地方 希望下次港隊嘅比賽會見到你地<br />\n黎緊亞洲盃外圍賽香港需要你地呀"},{"pid":"ff661ed1e950fcfb72541282d1bc66e64d277a94","tid":332141,"uid":9597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6fe213c771eda4fc1403b27550a2f460de340e","tid":332141,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想有一日港隊會好似今次咁要搶飛要早到排隊入場<br />\n會有球迷全場企起身為港隊打氣"},{"pid":"33a53aef6fe46f93405596cff401bb367baf39a8","tid":332141,"uid":4492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想有一日港隊會好似今次咁要搶飛要早到排隊入場<br />\n會有球迷全場企起身為港隊打氣</blockquote><br />\n除咗再對支那之外都幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855cb82ae7184e45c9d02d84ac2788f10a6bd082","tid":332141,"uid":33770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想有一日港隊會好似今次咁要搶飛要早到排隊入場<