":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想有一日港隊會好似今次咁要搶飛要早到排隊入場<br />\n會有球迷全場企起身為港隊打氣</blockquote><br />\n除咗再對支那之外都幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實港隊真係幾正<br />\n樂仔對北泡入波我仲興奮過今次古天奴入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個刻真係好正 俾左一陣以為會贏到嘅希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌下半場開波唔集中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其餘時間都踢得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e59660c972b75a6439f99f39a9a259cc468154","tid":332141,"uid":104423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:24:07.000Z","msg":"會黎支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aed88bcfc2cbcc0b2cc1c66ac4cd78817b08fdb","tid":332141,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係亞協杯南華對西亞狗最團結最有氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成盒雞喺上面飛落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be75154a13a88bd560f2b29f2c5a5ea0bb0c0341","tid":332141,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T18:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想有一日港隊會好似今次咁要搶飛要早到排隊入場<br />\n會有球迷全場企起身為港隊打氣</blockquote><br />\n試過喇<br />\n政治波<br />\n仲要只限旺角細場<br />\n有啲野唔係一時三刻改變到<br />\n港隊就因為香港人拎番個身份,而撐港隊<br />\n地區足球呢<br />\n你睇下百年老會南華<br />\n比人搞到自我降班<br />\n有足總班友喺到,一日都唔會有好波睇</blockquote><br />\